			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Lithium concentrate is one of the various forms of lithium sold in the market. It is derived from hard rock mines or large pond systems that concentrate lithium from brine using evaporation. Lithium concentrate is used in the production of lithium compounds, such as lithium carbonate and lithium hydroxide, which are essential for manufacturing rechargeable batteries for electronics and electric vehicles.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">锂精矿是市场上销售的各种形式的锂之一。 它源自硬岩矿山或大型池塘系统，通过蒸发从盐水中浓缩锂。 锂精矿用于生产碳酸锂和氢氧化锂等锂化合物，这对于制造电子产品和电动汽车的充电电池至关重要。</common:generalComment>
